{
  "stem": "893.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we thought, let's go and approach the-- that Hungarian farmer, and tell him that we would like to get in touch with the ambassador and tell him that we are from Eastern Slovakia-- not the Jews, you know, God forbid that we should give up our identity-- that our parents live in Eastern Slovakia, and there was no way of getting to Eastern Slovakian.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whether he could take us through-- to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then from Hungary we'll go through Budapest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'll go back to Eastern Slovakia, because the Slovakian railroad was sabotaged by Russian and Slovakian partisans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, it was something that would have been believable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Several people were using the Hungarian railroads to go into Eastern Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we felt, once we are in Hungary, we'll go to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He, in turn, told us that he doesn't think that he would jeopardize his automobile.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's his baby.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The diplomat-- no, we didn't talk to the diplomat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The farmer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's not using it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's afraid that they'll-- that they'll either, the Hungarians or the Germans, will take it away from him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he wanted to sort of survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know that my paternal grand-uncle knew the-- that-- the ambassador.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He never told me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, when the round-up-- during the round-up, when they knocked on their door, that building belonged to my uncle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a five-storey building, just underneath the castle of-- of Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had a plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had two apartments-- one adjoining the other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they sort of had a hole in between the two apartments.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the plan was that every night they'll padlock the other apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was like an armoire where they kept their clothes, didn't have glass, that armoire, just, like, with a closet.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
